only one of them.

10:13.531 --> 10:15.783
The good news is,
they can't start breeding.

10:16.033 --> 10:20.788
The bad news, everyone, is, the
beast reproduces asexually.

10:20.871 --> 10:22.456
A single bone vampire,

10:22.540 --> 10:26.710
left alone with some quiet music
and some bone vampire porn,

10:26.794 --> 10:29.130
