have emotions, Fry.

11:14.925 --> 11:16.802
Its brain is
the size of a walnut.

11:17.052 --> 11:19.680
So are walnuts,
and they're delicious.

11:23.767 --> 11:27.396
I'll miss you, Mr. Peppy,
but you'll be happier here.

11:27.605 --> 11:28.814
(MUTTERING)

11:28.898 --> 11:30.900
So, go on, go.

11:31.525 --> 11:33.652
Goodbye, IW- Peppy-

11:33.736 --> 11:36.363
