12:37.841 --> 12:39.635
Behave yourselves, gents.

12:39.718 --> 12:42.263
Off-worlders best
be welcome here,

12:42.346 --> 12:45.349
especially if we're trying
to get the Olympics.

12:45.474 --> 12:46.850
(CLAMORING)

12:48.852 --> 12:50.271
May I buy you a drink?

12:50.354 --> 12:52.856
We don't get a lot of
pretty faces around here.

12:53.148 --> 12:54.275
